snippet.title: Undertale: No More Deals - Teaser
snippet.description:
Yes, Im not dead
As I promised, here is it
Things from teaser can be changed in future
If you're interested in project, I recomend to check out official gamejolt page
https://gamejolt.com/games/ut-nmd/398695
Oh, and also check out my discord server!
https://discord.gg/bgNAgFYVnS
